(183,61,"_elementor_data","[{\"id\":\"63de1159\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"595f81ca\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3bf009c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Ima Solution was founded in 2014 with a strong recognition of the fact that business issues need to be addressed in a systematized format. With extensive market research and experience of business-related problems, we found that:<\\/p><ul><li>Taking responsibility for decision-making is a key pain area for a majority of running businesses where some managers are constantly second-guessing their decisions<\\/li><li>Data is either not getting captured or utilized to its full potential<\\/li><li>Processes aren\\u2019t well-defined, documented and optimized<\\/li><li>Risks are not covered within the decision-making process making the business more prone to market threats<\\/li><li>Systems, technology, and communication channels are not in-line with business requirements<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Ima Solution was started as a journey to try and mitigate these pain-points. We help business leaders, managers and entrepreneurs make decisions confidently, backed by data and ingrained with real experience.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2dde56c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ecaf949\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a7c7d65\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title_text\":\"Moiz\",\"description_text\":\"A young, dynamic and quality leader who has an unreal fascination with numbers and data. He sees patterns in data and his love affair with data trends and analysis is long-standing. He is a business consultant with over 11 years of experience working with many Fortune 500 companies. Risk analysis, inclination to implement and improve the IT structure in organizations and customer-centricity make him a wholesome consultant. He started the business shrink phenomena and is known as a data whisperer by his close associates. \"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a17bd9a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"428d5d0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title_text\":\"Fatima\",\"description_text\":\"She has a background in marketing and finance and is placed as the strategic head of the company. Her strength is goal-management and is considered to be a great task-master. She is focused and driven towards achieving results. She brings her reflective nature into making sound marketing strategies by evaluating the strengths and weaknesses of your on-going program. She is often the one who creates process steps with her engineered approach and solves problems with a long-term perspective. \"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]"),
