(444,110,"_elementor_data","[{\"id\":\"1d0b1d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":700}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8183f18\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"739d3c3c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"Data matters! It is everywhere and one of the most important aspects of making business decisions. You have business data, right? Possibly accumulated over several years but are you utilizing the full potential of this gold-like valuable asset? Unfortunately, the answer to this question is \\u201cno\\u201d for most businesses. We love trusting our gut feeling and make emotional decisions on an impulse. The adrenaline feels awesome until it doesn\\u2019t. Then problems start to surface where you never thought you\\u2019d have one. The management of the business becomes heavier and more such emotion-based decisions are added to the operations. Resources are stretched, employees are overworked and revenues are just not cutting it.\\n\\nSounds familiar? Let\\u2019s start from the correct and optimal utilization of your business data to make better business decisions. Look at problems as potential opportunities. Don\\u2019t know how to do that? That\\u2019s where Ima Solution steps in. Take the help of our business shrinks and data whisperers who are able to get to the core of even the most unique problems. Engage with Ima Solution to come up with logically sequenced business steps which are well-thought of and give you the peace of mind to confidently take the business ahead. Chat with a professional business consultant to get solutions, whether your problem is to set up a business unit, expand geographically or put out everyday business fires. <em>Ima Solution<\\/em> is truly meant <em>for every business<\\/em>.\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2780625\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4414e4a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d7243d6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"About Us\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f0b25f6\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fa67627\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e2edcfd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Ima Solution was founded in 2014 with a strong recognition of the fact that business issues need to be addressed in a systematized format. With extensive market research and experience of business-related problems, we found that:<\\/p><ul><li>Taking responsibility for decision-making is a key pain area for a majority of running businesses where some managers are constantly second-guessing their decisions<\\/li><li>Data is either not getting captured or utilized to its full potential<\\/li><li>Processes aren\\u2019t well-defined, documented and optimized<\\/li><li>Risks are not covered within the decision-making process making the business more prone to market threats<\\/li><li>Systems, technology, and communication channels are not in-line with business requirements<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Ima Solution was started as a journey to try and mitigate these pain-points. We help business leaders, managers and entrepreneurs make decisions confidently, backed by data and ingrained with real experience.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"368514d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Meet our management team\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"36df642\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"068d63a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"57ae36c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[