(709,161,"_elementor_data","[{\"id\":\"5a5b3a73\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3f37d089\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8f3452c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>At Ima Solution, we recognize that business organizations run on people making effective decisions. Managers may indeed be capable of a lot but \\u201ceverything\\u201d might just be excessive. Often in this pursuit, they end up taking major chunks of work, juggling between activities at almost all times. While it might look like a lot of work is getting done, it is the quality of work that suffers. Not to mention those few burdened souls. This kind of over-working impacts a business leader on two fronts, personal and professional.<\\/p>\\n<p>At the professional front, decision making and operations are affected. A strategic vision is lost and even small business problems are amplified. A business consultation service touches even the personal aspect of this problem by making a lasting impact on running your business better. Ima Solution offers business consultation services in order to get you back on track and focus on the things that matter. The consultation is wholesome and based on data so that the path forward caters to specific individual requirements.<\\/p>\\n<p>A business consultant can help you manage change, optimize processes, learn about best practices, glide through a tough period, and infuse a fresh and creative take on your business. Ima Solution\\u2019s strong emphasis on data helps with evaluating the long-term impact of crucial business decisions. Chart a healthy way forward for yourself and get in touch with the Ima team today!<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]"),
