mized products<\\/li><li>Use existing data in a way that is meaningful for the business<\\/li><li>Integrate systems to form a manageable and cohesive workspace<\\/li><li>Keep the focus on internal and external customers<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Manage operation, maintain and track data to work in a world of enhanced capabilities and meet the ever-changing needs of running a business. An IT consultation is the key to your business growth. Get it right away.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"6beea49\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Marketing Consultation \",\"tab_content\":\"<p>A marketing consultation for your business segment can help you understand what is working for your business. You can also find out if what you spend on marketing activities is getting utilized effectively. The Ima consultant provides:<\\/p><ul><li>Branding<\\/li><li>Market positioning<\\/li><li>Digital media strategy<\\/li><li>Marketing health check-up and evaluation of current marketing campaigns<\\/li><li>Marketing Roadmap<\\/li><\\/ul><p>A confident marketing strategy is what keeps your business on track, so double checking that it is effective is appropriate. Contact Ima Solution for your marketing problems right away.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"131219b\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Content strategy\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Your business depends upon the content that you share with your internal and external stakeholders. Ima Solution helps you:<\\/p><ul><li>Build a content strategy for your company<\\/li><li>Create a content roadmap for the next year<\\/li><li>Create content for website, brochures, email marketing, presentations, PR posts, SEO pages, white papers and much more<\\/li><li>Edit and proofread existing content<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Content is king and talking about what your audiences want to know is most beneficial for your business. Get the Ima experts to create a content strategy for you now.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"5f8c703\"}],\"border_color\":\"#54595f\",\"tab_color\":\"#54595f\",\"background_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.04)\",\"tab_active_color\"