,\"size\":2}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"e1c7c5d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":20}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"9041698\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"tabs\":[{\"tab_title\":\"Strategic planning and management\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Want to chart out a plan ahead? Then it is essential to building in a strategic plan based on research and market knowledge. Strategic planning consultation includes:<\\/p><ul><li>Business plan<\\/li><li>Execution directives<\\/li><li>Market research<\\/li><li>Risk analysis<\\/li><li>Competition analysis<\\/li><li>Expert recommendations<\\/li><li>Price quotes<\\/li><li>Documentation and process steps<\\/li><li>Business set up<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Knowing that you are making an informed decision is by itself a great relief and then add to it the benefits of making good choices. Get in touch with the Ima experts today.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"248d909\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Business shrink\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Our business shrinks are here to listen to your business issues and offer researched recommendations. Ima Solution provides:<\\/p><ul><li>Problem analysis<\\/li><li>Business health check-up<\\/li><li>Quality control<\\/li><li>Business personnel management<\\/li><li>Customized solutions<\\/li><li>Data capture points<\\/li><li>Data analysis<\\/li><li>Implementing management theories into practice<\\/li><\\/ul><p>A problem addressed at the right time could make all the difference to the survival and growth of a company. Get a business shrink for your problems today.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"bbf820c\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Ops Consultation\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>This is often the responsible factor for poor performance even though a great plan was charted. Ima Solution helps with building processes through:<\\/p><ul><li>Tracking current process performance<\\/li><li>Mapping process steps<\\/li><li>Cost-benefit analysis<\\/li><li>Re-engineering processes<